Direct Known Subclasses:
LAtom, LError, LNumber, LPair, LString, NIL
public abstract class LValue
extends LExp

The LValue class is the abstract data-structure that defines all SkeletonLisp's value expressions.

The value expressions of SkeletonLisp are LAtom, LError, LId, LNumber, LPair, and NIL
